The paper deals with image denoising using deep neural networks, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of deep networks as priors, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG). The algorithm proposed in the paper involves optimization, which falls under information theory (cs.IT) and numerical analysis (cs.NA). Finally, the paper includes numerical experiments, which is a common topic in multimedia (cs.MM).
